name: OMEN
description: Parameters of 2 dimensions and 3 dimensions become biased when they enter the human brain. Non-figurative forms decorate the new reality, and along with the development of the era of digital transformation, help humans to create chaos that appears in the human brain and make it a collaboration together. The results of the work of the human brain and the era of digital transformation seem to be a sign that the human mind on form is no longer the same.
